  <description><![CDATA[<p>For those in search of pure relaxation beside the sea, the Club Hotel Baja Sardinia provides the perfect destination, in the <a data-udi="umb://document/10879313b41b457bb9a2212bd1747034" href="/{localLink:umb://document/10879313b41b457bb9a2212bd1747034}" title="Northern Sardinia">Costa Smeralda Area</a>. Located just a few metres from the crystal clear, turquoise waters of the bay of Cala Battistoni, the hotel has its own private area of sandy beach in the bay of Forte Cappellini that looks out over the islands of the Maddalena Archipelago. The small resort of Baja <a data-udi="umb://document/c7d9c305cd1e44568dec1178157bc9f9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c7d9c305cd1e44568dec1178157bc9f9}" title="Sardinia">Sardinia</a> is on your doorstep and swish Porto Cervo is a short drive away. </p>
<p>With three restaurants to choose from you are spoilt for choice with the superb dishes served. The Bouganville restaurant is the main restaurant where breakfast, lunch and dinner is served daily. Offering traditional Mediterranean and international dishes enriched by the fresh local produce. Miramare restaurant is located on the terrace and serves our guests dinner each evening during the summer months and the Casablanca a la carte restaurant's menu offers a refined and tasty cuisine with a selection of wines to compliment each dish (payable locally, not included in full board and half board catering).</p>
<p>Enjoy the warm evenings in the hotels garden at the Piano &amp; American bar providing a perfect blend of music and cocktails. The hotel offers a reserved area of the beach fully equipped and exclusive for our guests. The is also a snack bar located right on the beach.</p>
<p>Car hire is recommended for this hotel. Club Hotel Baja Sardinia is approx. 40 mins from Olbia airport</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
