  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>American bar and piano bar every evening in high season</li>
<li>3 restaurants, Bouganville, Miramare &amp; Casablanca</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pools &amp; Beaches</strong></span></p>
<p>The hotel offers a private beach for all guests in the beautiful bay in Forte Cappellini. The beach is located around 800 metres from the Club Hotel, reachable either on foot with a pleasant walk (please note that the path is unpaved) or with the free shuttle service available every day from 8 am to 8 pm. On the beach you'll find comfortable sunbeds, umbrellas, a snack bar and lifeguard service. The hotel can provide beach towels. </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Activities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Boat trips (local charge)</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Practical Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Car parking available </li>
<li>24hr concierge service </li>
<li>Free WiFi available in the rooms and public areas</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></facilityDescription>
