  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard rooms </strong>are approximately, 18-24m² and sleep two people, with extra beds available for one adult or two children (sofa or bunk beds). They are either located in the main building or the annex and have a full equipped balcony or terrace. All rooms have private bath or shower, air conditioning, television, minibar, safe and hairdryer.</p>
<p><strong>Standard sea view</strong> <strong>rooms </strong>are approximately, 18-24m² with a balcony or terrace overlooking the sea. These rooms sleep two people with a third bed available on request. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are approximately, 20-26m² and have a small living corner. These rooms are located on the second floor in the annex. These rooms sleep two people with extra beds available with e<span>xtra beds available for one adult, or two children, or one child &amp; an infant. </span></p>
<p><strong>Single rooms </strong>are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
